Output docs/assets/aisnitch-demo.gif

Require node

Set Shell "zsh"
Set Theme "TokyoNightStorm"
Set FontSize 22
Set Width 1500
Set Height 900
Set Padding 24
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Framerate 30
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Type "cd /Users/vava/Documents/GitHub/AutoSnitch"
Enter
Sleep 700ms

Type "node dist/cli/index.js start --mock all --mock-duration 18"
Enter

Sleep 4s
Type "v"
Sleep 1200ms
Down 3
Sleep 1200ms
PageDown
Sleep 1200ms
Ctrl+C
Sleep 1s
